title: Tibia Multi Ip Changer 7.1 - 8.11
description:
This IP Changer is a tool to change the IP, which your Tibia Client should connect to. It&#039;s for all versions from Tibia 7.1 to Tibia 8.11.
It has also got a new AUTO VERSION FINDER function, so it will automatically detect which version you want to change the IP for.


Install Notes:

- Download
- Unpack with WinRAR
- Double-click &#039;Installer.exe&#039; and install it step by step
- Open your Tibia Client and the IP Changer and select and Open Tibia server.


Visit

http://otservlist.org/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
